President Obama has nominated Judge Nancy B. Firestone, Lydia Kay Griggsby, and Thomas L. Halkowski to serve on the United States Court of Federal Claims. Judge Firestone has served as a Judge of the United States Court of Federal Claims since 1998 and has a background in environmental law. Lydia Kay Griggsby has been the Chief Counsel for Privacy and Information Policy for the United States Senate Committee on the Judiciary since 2008. Thomas L. Halkowski is a Principal in the Delaware office of Fish & Richardson, P.C. and primarily handles patent litigation.